MCA_COMM - Versions history

Version 1.2.0 from 11.05.2022

Changes since initial version from 05.01.2022:

GBS_MCA_Comm:
- new: struct QUERY_STATE527_EX
- new: E_ERROR_FLAG MMCA_SET_FLAT_TOP_TIME(uint16_t FlatTopTime);
- new: E_ERROR_FLAG MMCA_QUERY_STATE527_EX(struct QUERY_STATE527_EX* rec_data);
- additional parameter for MMCA_SET_PZC_MANUAL: bool HighPrecision = true;
  (offset is returned with higher precision, should be true for an MCA-527 
  with firmware version 12.05. or higher) 

GBS_MCA_Data:
- new: uint16_t GetMaxFlattop(struct McaComm::QUERY_STATE527*, struct McaComm::QUERY_STATE527_EX*);
- additional blocks are written to spe file:
  $SPEC_REM:
  $FLAT_TOP:
  $FAST_DISCR:
  $SLOW_DISCR:
  $PUR:
  $STAB:
  $STAB_PARAM:
  $POWER:
  $MCA_REPEAT:
  $TDF:
  $REC_COUNTER:
  $REC_ERROR_COUNTER:
- small bugfix in output of block $POWER_STATE: in spe file

GBS_MCA_Cmd:
- new command set_flattop_time <time> - set flattop time
- additional parameter comment for save command
- additional command set_pzc auto - evaluate PZC automatically by offset minimization
- additional command query_state - show state information on the MCA

